outputs.output_descr:
1: An operational national regulatory and institutional framework on ABS.
2: Strengthened national institutional and stakeholder capacity for implementation of the national ABS framework.
3: Best practice ABS processes (three) are demonstrated recognizing the principles of PIC and Mutually Agreed Terms (MAT)
including the fair and equitable sharing of benefits.

project_descr: Developing and Implementing a National Access and Benefit Sharing Framework in Malaysia
project_title: PIMS 5191 National Access and Benefit Sharing Framework
